title: Statement on the Visit of Crown Prince Mohammed bin Zayed Al Nahyan of the United Arab Emirates | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House
Office of the Press Secretary


For Immediate Release
April 22, 2011

 



Statement on the Visit of Crown Prince Mohammed bin Zayed Al Nahyan of the United Arab Emirates




President Obama will welcome Crown Prince Mohammed bin Zayed Al Nahyan of the United Arab Emirates to the White House on Tuesday, April 26th.Â  The President looks forward to discussing with the Crown Prince the strong ties between the United States and the UAE and our common strategic interests in the region.
